snippet.title: Mixed Feelings 2: Elysium Trailer
snippet.description:
Following the events of Mixed Feelings, Elysium brings you down the same river you've been down again, again, and again. However, this time, you decide to take a turn, finding yourself on the opposite end of Asphodel Meadows.

Upon meeting Ezra, Zale, and Dandy, you discover that you don't remember who you are, where you came from, or why you're even there. The story unfolds as the residents of the town try and help you remember, and you learn what it truly means to be yourself.

Mixed Feelings: http://spoonycatt.itch.io/mixed-feelings
Mixed Feelings 2: Elysium: http://spoonycatt.itch.io/mixed-feelings-elysium
Music by casejackal http://case.dog/music
